entry.title: Combined summary - Release of bitcoin-s 1.9.1
entry.summary: Bitcoin-s, a set of bitcoin libraries written in Scala, has recently released version 1.9.1. The project is designed to follow the Discreet Log Contract specification and users can find more information about it at bitcoin-s.org or refer to the release notes for the updated version. The updated libraries can be accessed through GitHub at https://github.com/bitcoin-s/bitcoin-s/releases/tag/1.9.1.
